==相關詞語==
在討論護理霸凌時，也常會提到水平暴力（Horizontal Violence）<ref>{{cite web|last=Roy|first=Josie|title=Horizontal Violence|url=http://nursing.advanceweb.com/editorial/content/editorial.aspx?cc=102740|publisher=ADVANCE for Nurses|accessdate=5 October 2011|archive-date=2016-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223125244/http://nursing.advanceweb.com/editorial/content/editorial.aspx?cc=102740|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這個詞的意思是在護理環境下，來自同事的霸凌，這會讓工作環境充滿壓力且不悅。另一個詞是橫向暴力（lateral violence），描述霸凌對象是在工作場合層級較低的人，避免對方有機會再往上爬。

==補救措施==
有些醫療機構計劃教育員工及醫護團隊成員如何提升社會互動、適當的職場禮儀，及在工作場所的正向{{le|人際交往能力|people skills}}。護理人員有權因受到霸凌而獲得金錢補償<ref name=Trossman>{{cite journal |pmid=19024048 |year=2008 |last1=Trossman |first1=S |title=Behaving badly? Joint Commission issues alert aimed at improving workplace culture, patient care |volume=40 |issue=5 |pages=1, 6, 12 |journal=The American nurse}}</ref><ref name=Martin>{{cite journal |url=http://www.soakitupspeaking.com/userfiles/file/IsYourHospitalSafe.pdf |pages=21–8 |doi=10.3200/HTPS.86.3.21-28 |title=Is Your Hospital Safe? Disruptive Behavior and Workplace Bullying |year=2008 |last1=Martin |first1=William |journal=Hospital Topics |volume=86 |issue=3 |pmid=18694856 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308023152/http://www.soakitupspeaking.com/userfiles/file/IsYourHospitalSafe.pdf |archivedate=2012-03-08 |access-date=2016-02-16 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.injury-compensation-zone.co.uk/nurse-work-injury-compensation/ Nurse Work Injury Compensation]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} Eoin Campbell Injury Compensation Zone</ref><ref name=Kerfoot>{{cite journal |pmid=19248414 |year=2008 |last1=Kerfoot |first1=KM |title=Leadership, civility, and the 'no jerks' rule |volume=17 |issue=6 |pages=441–2 |journal=Medsurg nursing}}</ref>。

